$interpreted: Aosta: You had a...conversation with the monster!? And you made peace with it!?
Nolva: More or less. Waverlyde said that from now on, whenever I fall into a deep slumber, he will take control of my body to protect me.
Aosta: Waverlyde?
Nolva: After all, we are sharing the same body. He said that if I died, he would be quite troubled as well.
Nolva: Also, about assaulting people who held grudges against me, I've already scolded him about that. He promised me that he won't do that again.
Aosta: So you even gave the monster inside you a name...
Aosta: Hmph, how amusing.
Nolva: Thank you so much for giving me that medicine. If not for that, I wouldn't be able to know the truth behind all this...
Nolva: You are indeed a good doctor~!
Aosta: You can interpret my actions however you want. I was merely doing research on a void disease specimen.
Aosta: As for the medicine, I won't be able to make another one any time soon. So if you fall asleep in the near future, you won't be able to sense him.
Nolva: That's fine. I believe that he will keep his word. After all, Waverlyde is my very first friend.
Aosta: Even though I can't completely cure your void disease, I can more or less control the frequency of your symptoms.
Aosta: If you don't feel well, pay me a visit.
Nolva: Understood. Thank you, Dr. Clovis. I shall take my leave. See you next time!
Experiment: Gao~ Gao~!
Nolva: You too, little MX46. Goodbye~!
Aosta: Hmph, another eccentric patient...what do you think?
Experiment: Gao~ Gao~
Kittyeyes: ...That's strange. Where is this place...
Nolva: Umm... do you need help?
Kittyeyes: Oh, thank you. I have a shipment that needs to be delivered to the east village located on the Prairie. However, I just couldn't find it anywhere.
Nolva: The east village? That's where I live~
Nolva: How about you follow behind me? I can take you there.
Kittyeyes: Really? Thank you so much. You're my saving grace!
Grandpa: That's it, Nolva. Open your heart.
Nolva: Grandpa!?
Kittyeyes: What? What are you looking at?
Nolva: Nothing...let's go.
Kittyeyes: Hmm~ Ah, right; I am Kittyeyes. I just moved into the shack nearby with my brother. What's your name?
Nolva: I'm Nolva Carpenter.
Kittyeyes: Then I'll call you sister Nolva~ You're a nice person. Maybe we can be good friends!
Nolva: Haha, really?
Kittyeyes: Really~! I'm serious!
Nolva: Haha~!
